      "comment": "CREATING (7) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 8 lengths (25.56) at Geelong. Rates on top again. RIPPER RAE (3) flew the lids with a strong early split and led throughout to score an impressive win by 2 lengths over 500m at Bendigo (28.03). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of the leading chances again. NARINGAL LAD (1) drifted back settling but did best work late to finish 5th at Warrnambool over 450m (25.90). Yet to win here but has run some good races. Can measure up this time. IMPRESS CARTER (6) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
